{"id":1735097,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:15.082Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735097,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Cinta Samar TV1","overview":"# The Journey of Azli  The story follows the life journey of Azli, who did not complete his studies in urban planning due to financial problems. Because of his strong interest in luxury cars, he agrees to become a personal driver to a contractor, Hisham. After two months on the job, he impersonates the company's Operations Director while Hisham is on vacation and meets Juliana, the daughter of Tan Sri Malik. After they fall in love and promise to be together for life, and are introduced to Tan Sri Malik, Azli begins to feel guilty and regretful about his actions. He confesses to Juliana that he is actually just a driver impersonating a businessman. Juliana does not believe him and accuses Azli of deceiving her and tries to escape from him. Tan Sri Malik also does not believe him based on his appearance, his driving of luxury cars, and his extensive knowledge of real estate business dealings. In fact, Juliana falls ill due to her disappointment and longing for Azli.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/ms6yVmpJxPq1VNFYBsDPeoiYEll.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Cinta Samar TV1","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":559402,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Amar Asyraf","original_name":"Amar Asyraf","popularity":0.1783,"profile_path":"/V3pYlbIrDANLcoVoeF8dD38XDQ.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ebf1cc4bbc831a0332e81","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1824721,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Syatilla Melvin